Hey its an alright lager. Served really golden with a clear white head. Goes down smoothly. Didnt realise it was produced by Dreher
Probably one of the best Hungarian lagers i tried
Enjoy

Yept, It has to be one of my favourite beers from my time in Budapest.

Enjoy!
